      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", brother of Alexander and son of Simon the Cyrenian. Alexander and Rufus are apparently named by St Mark as well known in the Christian Church, and it is observable that his Gospel was probably written at ",
        "children": []
