        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Lit. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "the chosen one",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", &c. All true Christians might be so described, (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Romans 8:33",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ",) but this, as Meyer remarks, would not forbid a special and emphatic use of the word, in the case of a Christian remarkable for character or usefulness.",
