        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] Evidently, the mother of Rufus (possibly the wife of Simon the Cyrenian,) had endeared herself to St Paul by special Christian kindness; the sweeter to him as his own parents, probably, were long departed.",
